u are required to build and containerize a simple Machine Learning application 
using Linear Regression in Python.
The application should predict salary based on years of experience using a 
small sample dataset. The entire project must run inside a Docker container.


A company wants to estimate an employee’s salary based on years of experience.
You are given the following dataset:

Years of Experience	  Salary (in lakhs)
-------------------  --------------------
1						3
2						5
3						7
4						9
5						11

The company wants to predict the salary for 6 years of experience.

folder structure
----------------------------
docker_lr/
│
├── app.py
├── requirements.txt
└── Dockerfile

Expected output:
------------------------------
Predicted salary for 6 years experience: 13.0